  <entry>
    <title>在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink</title>
    <link href="https://blog.dondaha.top/posts/pio-stm32-daplink/"/>
    <id>https://blog.dondaha.top/posts/pio-stm32-daplink/</id>
    <published>2024-12-05T07:19:21.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-12-05T07:22:29.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink"><a href="#在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink" class="headerlink" title="在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink"></a>在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink</h1><p>修改<code>platformio.ini</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">[env:genericSTM32F103C8]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">platform</span> = ststm32</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">board</span> = genericSTM32F103C8</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">framework</span> = ardui<span class="literal">no</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">upload_protocol</span> = cmsis-dap</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可直接upload</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;在PlatformIO中编程STM32时使用DAPLink&quot;&gt;&lt;/a</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
